<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body {
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }
  .info {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    padding: 0 .2em;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .signature-block {
    margin-top: 3em;
    margin-bottom: 3em;
  }
  .signature-field {
    min-height: 25px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
  }
  .form {
    border: 1px solid #000;
  }
  .form td {
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    border-right: 1px solid #000;
  }
  .form tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .form td:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .form label {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .form td p {
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 2px 0 4px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .article {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }
  .article label {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .article p {
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 2px 0 4px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .details {
    display: flex;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Reservation Agreement</h1>

  <p>This document defines agreement between Bukit Vista as accommodation provider and guest of the accommodation. This document was signed by <span class="info"><%=name%></span>to represent the guest (Guest) and PT Bukit Vista Nusantara as property manager for the accommodation (Management).</p>

  <div class="article">
    <h3>Reservation Details</h3>
    <div class="details">
      <p>Guest name: <%= name %></p>
      <p>Check in date: <%= checkIn %></p>
      <p>Check out date: <%= checkOut %></p>
      <p>Property name: <%= propertyName %></p>
    </div>
</div>

  <div class="article">
      <h3>Security deposit</h3>
      <p>We will send out a copy of the agreement, make sure this is your real email address.</p>
      <p>We will send out a copy of the agreement, make sure this is your real email address.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="article">
      <h3>Cancellation policy</h3>
      <p>We will send out a copy of the agreement, make sure this is your real email address.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="article">
      <h3>House rules</h3>
      <p>We will send out a copy of the agreement, make sure this is your real email address.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="article">
      <h3>Damage coverage</h3>
      <p>We will send out a copy of the agreement, make sure this is your real email address.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-block">
    <p><%= date %></p>
    <p class="signature-field"><img src="<%= signature %>" height="55"></p>
    <p><%= name %></p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
